amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: Bundles\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Void Mayonnaise is not used in any <a href=\"/Bundles\" title=\"Bundles\">bundles</a>.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Recipes\">Recipes</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/mediawiki/index.php?title=Void_Mayonnaise&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"Edit section: Recipes\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<table class=\"wikitable sortable roundedborder\">\n\n<tbody><tr>\n<th class=\"unsortable\">Image\n</th>\n<th>Name</th>\n<th>Description</th>\n<th>Ingredients</th>\n<th>Energy&#160;/ Health</th>\n<th>Recipe Source(s)</th>\n<th>Sell Price\n</th></tr>\n<tr>\n<td><div class=\"center\"><div class=\"floatnone\"><a href=\"/File:Strange_Bun.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Strange Bun.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/5/5e/Strange_Bun.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"48\" height=\"48\" /></a></div></div>\n</td>\n<td><a href=\"/Strange_Bun\" title=\"Strange Bun\">Strange Bun</a>\n</td>\n<td>What's inside?\n</td>\n<td><link rel=\"mw-deduplicated-inline-style\" href=\"mw-data:TemplateStyles:r120955\"/><span class=\"nametemplate\"><img alt=\"Wheat Flour.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/2/2c/Wheat_Flour.png/24px-Wheat_Flour.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/2/2c/Wheat_Flour.png/36px-Wheat_Flour.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/2/2c/Wheat_Flour.png 2x\" /> <a href=\"/Wheat_Flour\" title=\"Wheat Flour\">Wheat Flour</a>&#160;(1)</span><link rel=\"mw-deduplicated-inline-style\" href=\"mw-data:TemplateStyles:r120955\"/><span class=\"nametemplate\"><img alt=\"Periwinkle.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/1/1d/Periwinkle.png/24px-Periwinkle.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/1/1d/Periwinkle.png/36px-Periwinkle.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/1/1d/Periwinkle.png 2x\" /> <a href=\"/Periwinkle\" title=\"Periwinkle\">Periwinkle</a>&#160;(1)</span><link rel=\"mw-deduplicated-inline-style\" href=\"mw-data:TemplateStyles:r120955\"/><span class=\"nametemplate\"><img alt=\"Void Mayonnaise.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/f/f3/Void_Mayonnaise.png/24px-Void_Mayonnaise.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/f/f3/Void_Mayonnaise.png/36px-Void_Mayonnaise.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/f/f3/Void_Mayonnaise.png 2x\" /> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Void Mayonnaise</a>&#160;(1)</span>\n</td>\n<td data-sort-value=\"0040\"><img alt=\"Energy.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/a/a9/Energy.png/24px-Energy.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/a/a9/Energy.png/36px-Energy.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/a/a9/Energy.png 2x\" /> 100<br /><img alt=\"Health.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/9/94/Health.png/24px-Health.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/9/94/Health.png/36px-Health.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/9/94/Health.png 2x\" /> 45\n</td>\n<td><p><img alt=\"Shane Icon.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/b/b4/Shane_Icon.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" /> <a href=\"/Shane\" title=\"Shane\">Shane</a>&#160;(Mail - 7+ <img alt=\"HeartIconLarge.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/0/04/HeartIconLarge.png/16px-HeartIconLarge.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/0/04/HeartIconLarge.png/24px-HeartIconLarge.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/thumb/0/04/HeartIconLarge.png/32px-HeartIconLarge.png 2x\" />)</p>\n</td>\n<td data-sort-value=\"0225\"><span style=\"display: none;\">data-sort-value=\"225\"&gt;</span><span class=\"no-wrap\"><img alt=\"Gold.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/1/10/Gold.png/18px-Gold.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"18\" height=\"18\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/1/10/Gold.png/27px-Gold.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/thumb/1/10/Gold.png/36px-Gold.png 2x\" />225g</span>\n</td></tr>\n\n\n</tbody></table>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Tailoring\">Tailoring</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/mediawiki/index.php?title=Void_Mayonnaise&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" title=\"Edit section: Tailoring\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Void Mayonnaise can be used in the spool of the <a href=\"/2_Willow_Lane#Sewing_Machine\" title=\"2 Willow Lane\">Sewing Machine</a> to create the dyeable <a href=\"/Tailoring\" title=\"Tailoring\">Polka Dot Shirt</a>.  <a href=\"/File:Shirt272.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Shirt272.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/5/57/Shirt272.png/24px-Shirt272.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/5/57/Shirt272.png 1.5x\" /></a>  It can also be used as a red dye in the dye pots, located at <a href=\"/Emily\" title=\"Emily\">Emily</a>'s and <a href=\"/Haley\" title=\"Haley\">Haley</a>'s house, <a href=\"/2_Willow_Lane\" title=\"2 Willow Lane\">2 Willow Lane</a>.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Quests\">Quests</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/mediawiki/index.php?title=Void_Mayonnaise&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" title=\"Edit section: Quests\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li>Void Mayonnaise is required to complete the <a href=\"/Quests#Goblin_Problem\" title=\"Quests\">\"Goblin Problem\" Quest</a>. One must be gifted to the <a href=\"/Henchman\" title=\"Henchman\">Henchman</a> guarding the <a href=\"/Witch%27s_Hut\" title=\"Witch&#39;s Hut\">Witch's Hut</a>.</li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/mediawiki/index.php?title=Void_Mayonnaise&amp;action=edit&amp;section=6\" title=\"Edit section: History\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/Version_History#1.1\" title=\"Version History\">1.1</a>: Introduced.</li>\n<li><a href=\"/Version_History#1.4\" title=\"Version History\">1.4</a>: Removed from <a href=\"/Traveling_Cart\" title=\"Traveling Cart\">Traveling Cart</a> stock.  Can now be used in <a href=\"/Tailoring\" title=\"Tailoring\">Tailoring</a>.</li>\n<li><a href=\"/Version_History#1.6\" title=\"Version History\">1.6</a>: Reduced chance of catching Void Mayonnaise from the <a href=\"/Witch%27s_Swamp\" title=\"Witch&#39;s Swamp\">Witch's Swamp</a> from 25% to 5%.</li></ul>\n<table class=\"wikitable\" id=\"navbox\">\n<tbody><tr>\n<th colspan=\"2\"><a href=\"/Artisan_Goods\" title=\"Artisan Goods\">Artisan Goods</a>\n</th></tr>\n<tr>\n<th><a href=\"/Bee_House\" title=\"Bee House\">Bee House</a>\n</th>\n<td><a href=\"/Honey\" title=\"Honey\">Honey</a>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th><a href=\"/Cask\" title=\"Cask\">Cask</a>\n</th>\n<td><a href=\"/Beer\" title=\"Beer\">Beer</a> • <a href=\"/Cheese\" title=\"Cheese\">Cheese</a> • <a href=\"/Goat_Cheese\" title=\"Goat Cheese\">Goat Cheese</a> • <a href=\"/Mead\" title=\"Mead\">Mead</a> • <a href=\"/Pale_Ale\" title=\"Pale Ale\">Pale Ale</a> • <a href=\"/Wine\" title=\"Wine\">Wine</a>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th><a href=\"/Cheese_Press\" title=\"Cheese Press\">Cheese Press</a>\n</th>\n<td><a href=\"/Cheese\" title=\"Cheese\">Cheese</a> • <a href=\"/Goat_Cheese\" title=\"Goat Cheese\">Goat Cheese</a>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th><a href=\"/Keg\" title=\"Keg\">Keg</a>\n</th>\n<td><a href=\"/Beer\" title=\"Beer\">Beer</a> • <a href=\"/Coffee\" title=\"Coffee\">Coffee</a> • <a href=\"/Green_Tea\" title=\"Green Tea\">Green Tea</a> • <a href=\"/Juice\" title=\"Juice\">Juice</a> • <a href=\"/Mead\" title=\"Mead\">Mead</a> • <a href=\"/Pale_Ale\" title=\"Pale Ale\">Pale Ale</a> • <a href=\"/Wine\" title=\"Wine\">Wine</a>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th><a href=\"/Loom\" title=\"Loom\">Loom</a>\n</th>\n<td><a href=\"/Cloth\" title=\"Cloth\">Cloth</a>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th><a href=\"/Mayonnaise_Machine\" title=\"Mayonnaise Machine\">Mayonnaise Machine</a>\n</th>\n<td><a href=\"/Dinosaur_Mayonnaise\" title=\"Dinosaur Mayonnaise\">Dinosaur Mayonnaise</a> • <a href=\"/Duck_Mayonnaise\" title=\"Duck Mayonnaise\">Duck Mayonnaise</a> • <a href=\"/Mayonnaise\" title=\"Mayonnaise\">Mayonnaise</a> • <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Void Mayonnaise</a>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th><a href=\"/Oil_Maker\" title=\"Oil Maker\">Oil Maker</a>\n</th>\n<td><a href=\"/Oil\" title=\"Oil\">Oil</a> • <a href=\"/Truffle_Oil\" title=\"Truffle Oil\">Truffle Oil</a>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th><a href=\"/Preserves_Jar\" title=\"Preserves Jar\">Preserves Jar</a>\n</th>\n<td><a href=\"/Aged_Roe\" title=\"Aged Roe\">Aged Roe</a> • <a href=\"/Caviar\" title=\"Caviar\">Caviar</a> • <a href=\"/Jellies_and_Pickles\" title=\"Jellies and Pickles\">Jellies and Pickles</a>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th><a href=\"/Fish_Smoker\" title=\"Fish Smoker\">Fish Smoker</a>\n</th>\n<td><a href=\"/Smoked_Fish\" title=\"Smoked Fish\">Smoked Fish</a>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th><a href=\"/Dehydrator\" title=\"Dehydrator\">Dehydrator</a>\n</th>\n<td><a href=\"/Dried_Mushrooms\" title=\"Dried Mushrooms\">Dried Mushrooms</a> • <a href=\"/Dried_Fruit\" title=\"Dried Fruit\">Dried Fruit</a> • <a href=\"/Raisins\" title=\"Raisins\">Raisins</a>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Misc\n</th>\n<td><a href=\"/Maple_Syrup\" title=\"Maple Syrup\">Maple Syrup</a> • <a href=\"/Oak_Resin\" title=\"Oak Resin\">Oak Resin</a> • <a href=\"/Pine_Tar\" title=\"Pine Tar\">Pine Tar</a>  • <a href=\"/Mystic_Syrup\" title=\"Mystic Syrup\">Mystic Syrup</a>\n</td></tr>\n</tbody></table>\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260413230309\nCache expiry: 86400\nDynamic content: false\nComplications: []\nCPU time usage: 0.202 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.246 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 2959/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 36872/2097152 bytes\nTemplat