      "wikitext": "{{Infobox\n|eng         = Void Mayonnaise\n|source      = <ul><li>[[Artisan Goods]]</li><li>[[Fishing]] in [[Witch's Swamp]] (5% chance)</li></ul>\n|ingredients = {{name|Void Egg|1}}\n|quality     = false\n|sellprice   = 275\n|edibility   = -30\n|crafttime   = 3h\n|craftingstation = {{name|Mayonnaise Machine}}\n}}\n'''Void Mayonnaise''' is an [[Artisan Goods|Artisan Good]] made by placing a [[Void Egg]] inside the [[Mayonnaise Machine]]. It can also be obtained by [[fishing]] in the [[Witch's Swamp]] if the player does not have one in inventory and the [[Henchman]] is guarding the [[Witch's Hut]] (5% chance).\n\nGifting a Void Mayonnaise to the Henchman outside the [[Witch's Hut]] will allow players to pass during the quest [[Quests#Goblin Problem|Goblin Problem]].\n\n==Gifting==\n{{GiftsByItem\n|love=Krobus\n|hate=Sebastian,Jas,Vincent,Sam,Robin,Demetrius,Maru,Linus,Pierre,Abigail,Alex,George,Evelyn,Lewis,Clint,Penny,Pam,Emily,Haley,Jodi,Kent,Leah,Shane,Marnie,Elliott,Gus,Dwarf,Wizard,Harvey,Sandy,Willy,Caroline,Leo\n}}\n\n==Bundles==\nVoid Mayonnaise is not used in any [[bundles]].\n\n==Recipes==\n{{Recipes|header|hide=buff,duration}}\n{{:Strange Bun|RecipeRow/NoBuffs}}\n{{Recipes|footer}}\n\n==Tailoring==\nVoid Mayonnaise can be used in the spool of the [[2 Willow Lane#Sewing Machine|Sewing Machine]] to create the dyeable [[Tailoring|Polka Dot Shirt]].  [[File:Shirt272.png|24px]]  It can also be used as a red dye in the dye pots, located at [[Emily]]'s and [[Haley]]'s house, [[2 Willow Lane]].\n\n==Quests==\n*Void Mayonnaise is required to complete the [[Quests#Goblin Problem|\"Goblin Problem\" Quest]]. One must be gifted to the [[Henchman]] guarding the [[Witch's Hut]].\n\n==History==\n{{History|1.1|Introduced.}}\n{{History|1.4|Removed from [[Traveling Cart]] stock.  Can now be used in [[Tailoring]].}}\n{{History|1.6|Reduced chance of catching Void Mayonnaise from the [[Witch's Swamp]] from 25% to 5%.}}\n\n{{NavboxArtisanGoods}}\n\n[[Category: